longBusinessSummary: Kingston Resources Limited engages in the exploration, production, and evaluation of mineral properties in Australia and Papua New Guinea. The company's flagship project includes the Misima Gold project located in the Papua New Guinea. It also has interests in the Mineral Hill gold and copper mine located in Cobar, New South Wales. Kingston Resources Limited was incorporated in 1985 and is based in North Sydney, Australia.
